sections.text: poll books; contents.Beginning July 1, 2019, the electronic poll books for a precinct shall contain the list of registered voters and the sign-in register for the precinct combined in one database and shall include the registration information and the digital signatures for the registered voters of the precinct.SourceLaws 2018, LB1065, ยง 2.
